  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test

    public class CreateHabitEventTest
extends android.test.ActivityInstrumentationTestCase2<LoginActivity>
    The class for testing the CreateNewHabitEventFragment UI functions. These tests assume that there is a Jogging Habit in the database with a start date of April 20, 2016. Without this, some or all of these tests may fail. Note that this class does not test the ability to add images, since solo/robotium cannot navigate Android system UI.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    amckerna
